🎬5/10
CAPTAIN MARVEL
You walk into a resturant very hungry, you sit on the table and they give you a basket of bread and butter before your big tasty meal, that’s exactly what #CaptainMarvel is like, some people like bread and butter but I don’t. You’ll forget this movie when you wake up the next day, which to me is the worst type of movies because it didn’t leave any impact, good or bad. To me #BrieLarson didn’t play her role very well, I needed a much stronger performance, she just didn’t bring it, hopefully she’ll be much better in #AvengersEndGame also the camera work for this movie was very bad, they set up these great action scenes but you couldn’t SEE them because the camera movement and the editing was very fast. But on the up side
The story telling was good
#JudeLaw was great
#BenMendelsohn was amazing
And #SamuellJackson was the best

You’ll go see the movie anyways and you should because you wanna see how things get connected to Avengers End Game. This is not a BAD movie, this is just another superhero movie.
